* Validate Bundle
** Command
***_ databricks bundle validate
** Output
***_ Bundle name & target
***_ Workspace host & user
***_ Validation OK! or errors
** Error Types
***_ Missing required fields
***_ Invalid property names
***_ Unknown property warnings
** Best Practice
***_ Run after any config change
***_ Fix all errors before deploying
@endmindmap
